snippet.title: September Showcase Video
snippet.description:
Check out some of the latest and greatest games from the community on HiberWorld.com (https://hiberworld.com/) in this latest showcase video. At HiberWorld, there are thousands of new games to play each week, and everyone can create their own game to share with friends. Best of all, it's all free!

HiberWorld is free-to-play. Create, play, and share - all without the need to code. https://hiberworld.com/

Stay Connected:
►Twitter: http://bit.ly/hibertwitter
►Discord: http://bit.ly/hiberdiscord

If you enjoyed this content please subscribe and like this video!

Thanks for watching! 😊
